findings.title: Rounding error
findings.description: At some calculation with division, it goes first which can cause rounding errors because Solidity does not have floating points.

findings.title: Economical issue
findings.description: Burn address excluded from total supply counting, that means sum of the balances will not equal total supply.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to change TaxPerM, dev address, and withdraw ERC20 tokens and BNBs when the owner is not renounced.
